name: Portal
description: Trees always makes me think of roots that I have now and the ones I will grow someday. The tree bark has its own very unique pattern, such as the humans soul. It is said in many myths and legends of almost every culture that you can always find some magic portal in the Tree. The gates to the Unknown are made of wood, too. I believe that going through the magic portal will definitely lead you to you standing on the other side. "Portal" is featured in BIT.SHES Collection            iDENTITY |01| Vol.2 -All proceeds from this piece go to charitable organizations making a difference for positive change.
